{"id":1734632,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:46:39.976Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1734632,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi","overview":"# Halalkan Hati Yang Kucuri  The story of a young married couple, Faiq and Delisha, who share a passion for freedom, luxury, and unlimited fun. All advice given to them falls on deaf ears. When scolded by their families, they run away from home in a fit of anger. After a month, they return only to be shocked when their families suddenly disappear! The bungalow is sold and the family business changes ownership to someone else. Despite their efforts to find answers, they discover nothing. Their families are nowhere to be found, and their money is rapidly running out. Eventually, whether they like it or not, they are forced to start life from scratch as there is nothing left to sell. Now they understand that their family went bankrupt because of their wasteful lifestyle. They are forced to live as vagrants and are treated as beggars. They learn the meaning of hardship and self-reliance. Unexpectedly, Delisha becomes pregnant.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/4FO5PZGLTkVk2NdQ68s18UUjeLA.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2018-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1688485,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Aliff Aziz","original_name":"Aliff Aziz","popularity":0.769,"profile_path":"/74KCcxCYgfGqeL5eVkhMr327BSi.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5e2cb8b770396294f7e740","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1895424,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Farah Nabilah","original_name":"